name: Charles-Hubert- Paris  Dual Time Mechanical Pocket Watch
description:
Elegant piece of Charles Hubert Pocket Watch features 51 mm diameter, raised silver colored roman numerals, blue hour, minute and second hand. Chrome Plated stainless steel case, scratch resistant crystals, 17 jewel skeletonized mechanical movement with blue screws.


Dual time zone skeleton dial with roman numerals.

51 mm open face case with a matching curb chain.

Deluxe gift box.

Dial color: white.

Bezel Function: stationary.

Movement: mechanical-hand-wind.
